snippet.title: Warhaven - Official Release Date Trailer | gamescom ONL 2023
snippet.description:
"From War, To Haven" Check out the 90-second trailer introducing Blade, unveiled at the Gamescom ONL.
Have the opportunity to catch a glimpse of Blade's ultimate vengeance with a brisk tempo in the style of an engaging MV trailer.
